                                    <p class="oj-normal">“sustainability factors” means sustainability factors as defined in Article 2, point (24), of Regulation (EU) 2019/2088 of the European Parliament and of the Council<a id="ntc*1-L_2021277EN.01001401-E0008" href="#ntr*1-L_2021277EN.01001401-E0008"
                                          > (<span class="oj-super oj-note-tag">*1</span>)</a>;</p>
